---Makfile Options---

build files: make build 
clean files: make clean
zip files and test: make zip


---Execution Options---

./quadtree [-c threshold | -d | -m type | -o] [input_file1] [input_file2] [output_file]

-c : compression with the given threshold
-d : decompression
-m : mirror image
	 type: h   (horizontally)
		   v   (vertically)
-o : merge images (the second image is given through the input_file2 parameter)


!  All input_files must be P6 PPM files  !